---
title: Vegan Saucy Mushroom & Cabbage Bibimbap with Spicy Pickled Cucumber & Sesame Seeds
description: The only thing more fun than saying “bibimbap”? Eating it! Our vegan riff on this iconic Korean rice dish is positively bursting with flavorful veggies. Savory-sweet bulgogi-hoisin mushrooms are the meaty element, along with savory sautéed cabbage. Spicy pickled cucumbers add a bright, tangy crunch. They’re all arranged over a bed of steamy, fragrant rice, just waiting to be mixed up and savored with a generous sprinkle of nutty sesame seeds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-saucy-mushroom-cabbage-bibimbap-e57f3293.jpg
